title: Stepmania DDR 1-8 Random Movies + Scripts + Animations
description:
RandomMovies scripted by Ollec2004. Just kept a copy of the movies which I honestly don't remember where I got them from, it was back on 2005 or so.

Just copy the contents of the folder 'RandomMovies' to your RM folder within Stepmania and extract the 'Animations.zip' file to your 'Animations' folder within Stepmania.

I also included the scripts pack by Ollec2004 (SM.zip), use those scripts to enable the original movies per song.
